\fIBASE_DIR\fR
to form the new user\*(Aqs home directory name, if the
\fB\-d\fR
option is not used when creating a new account\&.
.sp
This option sets the
\fBHOME\fR
variable in
/etc/default/useradd\&.
.RE
.PP
